setnewwinprops (0.9) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Window setup sequence:
    - move to desktop
    - wait delay
    - change active desktop
    - wait for focus
    - set up remaining properties
  * add code to manage more properties:
    - shaded
    - sticky
  * more explanative messages

